---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import SectionHeader from "../../components/SectionHeader.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="LingMu UI/UX Prototype | Strategic Design">
	<main class="post-wrapper project-detail">
		<SectionHeader 
			tag="UI/UX / STRATEGIC DESIGN" 
			description="Interactive Prototype: Strategic sidebar navigation for immersive experience.">
			<h1 class="font-special text-5xl font-bold uppercase tracking-widest" style="margin: 1rem 0;">
				LingMu (灵沐)
			</h1>
		</SectionHeader>

		<section class="border-top" style="padding-top: 3rem;">
			<div class="content">
				<div class="project-intro-grid" style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); gap: 2rem; margin-bottom: 3rem;">
					<div>
						<h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">Strategic Shift</h3>
						<p style="line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-200);">
							为了优化在大屏端的交互体验，我们将导航栏移至<strong>左侧浮动区域</strong>。这一改动释放了底部视觉压力，使灵感记录过程更加沉浸且无遮挡。
						</p>
					</div>
					<div>
						<h3 style="margin-bottom: 0.8rem;">Deployment</h3>
						<p style="line-height: 1.8; color: var(--color-200);">
							原型通过 <strong>Vercel Edge Runtime</strong> 实时运行。左侧导航栏采用高斯模糊材质，确保在任何背景下都能保持清晰的层级关系。
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="lingmu-standalone-window">
					<div class="window-controls">
						<div class="window-dots"><span></span><span></span><span></span></div>
						<span class="window-title">LingMu Live Prototype (Sidebar Mode)</span>
					</div>
					<div class="window-body">
						<iframe 
							src="https://lingmu-app.vercel.app" 
							style="border: none; width: 100%; height: 100%; background: #000;" 
							allowfullscreen>
						</iframe>
					</div>
				</div>

				<p style="text-align: center; margin-top: 2rem; font-size: 0.85rem; color: var(--color-500); font-style: italic;">
					💡 提示：请点击左侧悬浮图标进行页面切换，内部内容可自由滑动。
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>
		<div style="height: 100px;"></div>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
	.project-detail {
		max-width: var(--max-width);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 var(--pad-inner);
	}

	.lingmu-standalone-window {
		width: 100%;
		height: 750px; /* 给予足够的高度 */
		background: #000;
		border-radius: 16px;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		overflow: hidden;
		border: 1px solid var(--border);
		box-shadow: 0 40px 100px rgba(0,0,0,0.5);
	}

	.window-controls {
		height: 42px;
		background: #1a1a1b;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		padding: 0 18px;
		gap: 20px;
		border-bottom: 1px solid #333;
	}

	.window-dots { display: flex; gap: 8px; }
	.window-dots span { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; background: #333; }
	.window-title { font-size: 11px; color: #777; font-family: monospace; letter-spacing: 0.5px; }

	.window-body { flex: 1; width: 100%; height: 100%; }

	@media (max-width: 767px) {
		.lingmu-standalone-window {
			height: 600px;
		}
	}
</style>
